WHERE authors1.id < authors2.id

queries.text:
SELECT
    c_smallint,
    c_boolean,
    c_integer,
    c_bigint,
    c_real,
    c_numeric,
    c_decimal,
    c_double_precision,
    c_money,
    c_date,
    c_time,
    c_timestamp,
    c_timestamp_with_tz,
    c_char,
    c_varchar,
    c_character_varying,
    c_text,
    c_bytea,
    COUNT(*) AS cnt
FROM postgres_types
GROUP BY
    c_smallint,
    c_boolean,
    c_integer,
    c_bigint,
    c_real,
    c_numeric,
    c_decimal,
    c_double_precision,
    c_money,
    c_date,
    c_time,
    c_timestamp,
    c_timestamp_with_tz,
    c_char,
    c_varchar,
    c_character_varying,
    c_text,
    c_bytea
LIMIT 1
queries.name: GetPostgresTypesCnt

queries.text:
SELECT
    MAX(c_integer) AS max_integer,
    MAX(c_varchar) AS max_varchar,
    MAX(c_timestamp) AS max_timestamp
FROM postgres_types
queries.name: GetPostgresFunctions
